'''Sheyf''' was the title for the commander of the [[Kiffu Guardians]] and the ruler of the planets [[Kiffu/Legends|Kiffu]] and [[Kiffex/Legends|Kiffex]]. From [[331 BBY]], sheyfs were members of the [[Clan Vos|Vos family]], until the planets were overrun by the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]. The sheyf's word was absolute.

Known sheyfs included [[Kurlin Vos]],<ref name="JvS">[[Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force (real-life book)|''Jedi vs. Sith: The Essential Guide to the Force'']]</ref> [[Tinté Vos]] and [[Zharia Vos]].

